1
00:00:25,600 --> 00:00:28,160
You actually dare to still be alive?

2
00:00:28,160 --> 00:00:29,280
Li Jing.

3
00:00:29,280 --> 00:00:31,600
Is this your answer?

4
00:00:32,280 --> 00:00:34,280
I, Li Jing, stand with Chentang Pass.

5
00:00:35,360 --> 00:00:36,520
Not a single step back.

6
00:00:36,520 --> 00:00:37,680
Li Jing, you brat!

7
00:00:37,680 --> 00:00:40,400
I knew you'd cling to life in fear.

8
00:00:40,400 --> 00:00:41,600
Old loach.

9
00:00:41,880 --> 00:00:43,800
What did you just call me?

10
00:00:44,720 --> 00:00:45,800
Your scheming...

11
00:00:45,800 --> 00:00:46,880
...is practically slapping me in the face.

12
00:00:47,400 --> 00:00:48,280
You don't actually...

13
00:00:48,280 --> 00:00:49,360
...think you're smart, do you?

14
00:00:49,360 --> 00:00:51,240
Old loach.

15
00:00:51,240 --> 00:00:52,840
You know, he really does look like one!

16
00:00:54,960 --> 00:00:56,160
Shut up!

17
00:00:56,400 --> 00:00:57,760
Look, look! He's getting anxious!

18
00:00:57,760 --> 00:00:58,760
Stop laughing!

19
00:01:00,880 --> 00:01:02,960
Crush Chentang Pass for me!

20
00:01:02,960 --> 00:01:04,680
Annihilate the Nine Provinces!

21
00:01:23,840 --> 00:01:24,720
What do we do?

22
00:01:24,720 --> 00:01:26,160
Such high waves!

23
00:01:26,720 --> 00:01:27,520
Li Jing.

24
00:01:28,760 --> 00:01:30,440
Is it time to use it now?

25
00:01:31,040 --> 00:01:31,760
Yes.

26
00:01:33,080 --> 00:01:33,800
Mystical Bird.

27
00:01:33,800 --> 00:01:34,640
Aid me!

28
00:01:39,320 --> 00:01:40,040
Li Jing!

29
00:01:40,040 --> 00:01:40,760
Come quickly!

30
00:01:51,160 --> 00:01:52,160
Your Highness.

31
00:01:52,720 --> 00:01:54,200
It's the aura of the Mystical Bird.

32
00:01:54,960 --> 00:01:55,880
The Mystical Bird.

33
00:01:57,560 --> 00:01:58,680
I've been waiting for it.

34
00:01:58,960 --> 00:02:01,760
The Seven Swords stand with Chentang Pass against the enemy!

35
00:02:05,280 --> 00:02:06,120
Boundless Heaven and Earth!

36
00:02:06,120 --> 00:02:07,280
Universe, lend me power!

37
00:02:09,480 --> 00:02:10,800
Heaven-Earth Formation!

38
00:02:11,480 --> 00:02:12,200
Rise!

39
00:02:26,680 --> 00:02:28,400
Formations, formations!

40
00:02:28,680 --> 00:02:30,640
Why is it always formations?

41
00:02:33,800 --> 00:02:34,840
Crown Prince!

42
00:02:34,840 --> 00:02:35,960
You absolutely must not!

43
00:02:37,640 --> 00:02:38,760
Brother!

44
00:02:39,440 --> 00:02:40,800
Wake up!

45
00:03:09,480 --> 00:03:10,320
This...

46
00:03:10,320 --> 00:03:11,960
What is this?

47
00:03:12,920 --> 00:03:13,680
What is this thing?

48
00:03:13,800 --> 00:03:14,640
We're in trouble.

49
00:03:14,640 --> 00:03:16,200
This seems to be a Demonic Dragon.

50
00:03:16,800 --> 00:03:17,440
A Demonic Dragon?

51
00:03:17,720 --> 00:03:18,400
What Demonic Dragon?

52
00:03:19,240 --> 00:03:20,040
Legend has it...

53
00:03:20,040 --> 00:03:22,400
The East Sea Dragon Palace once had a Crown Prince...

54
00:03:23,040 --> 00:03:25,400
...who tried to usurp the Dragon King and attack the Heavenly Court.

55
00:03:25,680 --> 00:03:26,920
After the plot failed...

56
00:03:27,040 --> 00:03:29,280
...he was sealed by the East Sea Dragon King in a demonic cave beneath the sea.

57
00:03:29,640 --> 00:03:30,520
Perhaps...

58
00:03:30,520 --> 00:03:31,920
...this is that Demonic Dragon.

59
00:03:34,480 --> 00:03:35,360
What do we do?

60
00:03:35,360 --> 00:03:36,440
What trump cards do we have left?

61
00:03:37,320 --> 00:03:38,480
There is one last move.

62
00:03:38,800 --> 00:03:39,280
Then...

63
00:03:39,280 --> 00:03:40,200
Then what are we waiting for?

64
00:03:42,840 --> 00:03:43,760
Waiting for the wind.

65
00:03:57,840 --> 00:04:00,000
It is time.

66
00:04:24,520 --> 00:04:26,680
This is the Bow of Heaven and Earth and Heaven-Shaking Arrow from the ancestral temple.

67
00:04:26,920 --> 00:04:27,880
This is the Bow of the Human Race.

68
00:04:28,600 --> 00:04:30,000
The Arrow of Slaughter.

69
00:04:44,520 --> 00:04:45,760
The final arrow.

70
00:05:05,160 --> 00:05:06,520
This place...

71
00:05:06,520 --> 00:05:08,240
...is Chentang Pass.

72
00:05:09,520 --> 00:05:12,040
Our race is at war with the Human Race.

73
00:05:13,000 --> 00:05:14,760
That human...

74
00:05:14,760 --> 00:05:16,080
State your name!

75
00:05:17,400 --> 00:05:19,120
Li Jing of Chentang Pass.

76
00:05:19,600 --> 00:05:21,960
Thank you for helping me awaken.

77
00:05:22,680 --> 00:05:24,520
To show my gratitude...

78
00:05:26,360 --> 00:05:28,760
...I'll give you a quick death.

79
00:05:30,040 --> 00:05:31,520
Seven Swords, unite!

80
00:05:32,360 --> 00:05:33,960
Heaven-Earth Formation!

81
00:05:34,120 --> 00:05:35,160
Heaven-Earth Formation!

82
00:05:50,480 --> 00:05:51,080
Yuhan.

83
00:05:51,080 --> 00:05:51,960
Don't!

84
00:05:58,200 --> 00:05:59,000
Li Jing!

85
00:05:59,840 --> 00:06:01,040
Chentang Pass...

86
00:06:01,600 --> 00:06:02,320
...must not fall!

87
00:06:10,880 --> 00:06:12,120
This is a space-time tunnel.

88
00:06:15,680 --> 00:06:16,480
No...

89
00:06:16,720 --> 00:06:17,880
This is an illusory world.

90
00:06:28,040 --> 00:06:28,640
Li Jing!

91
00:06:28,760 --> 00:06:29,400
Take the arrow!

92
00:06:32,680 --> 00:06:33,400
Li Jing!

93
00:06:36,080 --> 00:06:38,040
I've done my best.

94
00:06:42,440 --> 00:06:44,120
I sacrifice my life...

95
00:06:45,120 --> 00:06:47,400
...to burn my true spirit!

96
00:06:48,320 --> 00:06:50,360
Fall, Dragon!

97
00:07:02,040 --> 00:07:03,680
General Li shot the Demonic Dragon.

98
00:07:03,680 --> 00:07:04,400
We won!

99
00:07:04,400 --> 00:07:05,840
We won!

100
00:07:12,640 --> 00:07:13,640
The Mystical Bird.

101
00:07:13,880 --> 00:07:15,520
You're meddling.

102
00:07:16,080 --> 00:07:17,160
If I cause trouble, so be it.

103
00:07:17,600 --> 00:07:18,680
Stop spouting nonsense.

104
00:07:44,720 --> 00:07:45,520
Li Jing.

105
00:07:46,280 --> 00:07:46,880
Yuhan.

106
00:07:47,160 --> 00:07:48,440
My time

107
00:07:49,160 --> 00:07:50,440
is running out.
